Output docs/assets/near-manager-preview.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 680
Set FontSize 16
Set Framerate 12
Set PlaybackSpeed 1
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set TypingSpeed 25ms

Hide
Type "cd /tmp/NearManager && HOME=/tmp/NearManager near-fm --portable /tmp/near-manager-preview --shell docs/assets/near-manager-preview-shell.toml"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Show
Sleep 1s
Tab
Sleep 1s
Down@3
Sleep 1s
